a Elias","date":"November 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, set out to Tabuk and he left Ali behind. Ali said, \"You leave me behind with the women and children?\" The Prophet said, \"Are you not pleased in the same position for me as Aaron\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7625,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/dawah-hidayah-islam-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":27468,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: Guiding a person to Islam better than all wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy Allah, that Allah guides a man through you is better for you than a herd of expensive red camels.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3009, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2406 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25329,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/25\/no-second-wife-if-first-harmed\/","url_meta":{"origin":27468,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Polygamy: Do not marry second wife if first wife harmed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miswar ibn Makhramah reported: I heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say upon the pulpit, \u201cVerily, the sons of Hisham ibn al-Mughirah have sought my permission to marry their daughters to Ali ibn Abi Talib. I do not give permission, again, I do not give\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3927,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/31\/assume-prophet-righteous\/","url_meta":{"origin":27468,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Hadith: Assume the Prophet is most righteous, guided","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdur Rahman reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhen I narrate to you a tradition from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, assume from it that he is the most proper, the most guided, and the most righteous.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13481,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/10\/hasan-ibn-ali-makes-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":27468,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hasan: The Prophet\u2019s grandson Hasan ibn Ali makes peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis grandson of mine is a master. Perhaps Allah will reconcile two groups of Muslims through him.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u030